    <main>
      <h1>Bacon Egg and Cheese Bagel Recipe</h1>
      <p> Welcome to the straightfoward guide on how to make a Bacon Egg and Cheese Bagel! For memorable savory breakfast sandwich, follow this simple recipe everyone will love! </p>
        <a href="https://myeverydaytable.com/how-to-make-a-bacon-egg-and-cheese-bagel-breakfast-sandwich/"><img src=https://myeverydaytable.com/wp-content/uploads/bacon-egg-cheese-bagel.png alt="Bacon Egg and Cheese Bagel."></a>
      <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
         <ul>
          <li>Plain Bagel</li>
          <li>Butter</li>
          <li>Eggs</li>
          <li>Salt</li>
          <li>Bacon</li>
          <li>Cheese</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Heat 1/2 a tablespoon of butter in a pan</li>
          <li>Cook your eggs for about 3 minutes each side. Season with salt.</li>
          <li>Put cheese on top of eggs and move to the side.</li>
          <li>Cook your bacon.</li>
          <li>Toast your bagel.</li>
          <li>Assemble your sandwich.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>
